  zsh-autosuggestions-0.6.4.tar.gz::https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-autosuggestions/archive/v0.6.4.tar.gz
  https://github.com/starship/starship/releases/download/v0.47.0/starship-x86_64-unknown-linux-musl.tar.gz
